name: TC_IO_001 - Initial Verification of a New Investor
description:
**Test Scenario:**  
All the mandatory fields will be filled and form is submitted.

**Expected Result:**  
It should redirect to the Investor Profile page.

**How it is evaluated:**  
This is verified by checking the URL change; if initial verification is successful, 
the URL changes to `/InvestorProfile` from `/AddNewInvestor`.
